      <title>SEC 仍在考虑就新对冲基金规则在法庭上采取的下一步行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/sec-still-weighing-next-steps-in-court-over-new-hedge-fund-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国证券交易委员会主席加里·根斯勒称，华尔街最高监管机构仍在评估下一步措施，试图迫使对冲基金和私募股权公司披露更多有关其费用的信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/sec-still-weighing-next-steps-in-court-over-new-hedge-fund-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 19:27:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>博阿兹·温斯坦称拜登比特朗普更适合债券市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/boaz-weinstein-says-biden-is-better-for-bond-market-than-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[萨巴资本管理公司 (Saba Capital Management) 的博阿兹·温斯坦 (Boaz Weinstein) 在周二的彭博投资会议上表示，总统乔·拜登的连任对美国债券市场来说将比唐纳德·特朗普第二次担任总统更有利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/boaz-weinstein-says-biden-is-better-for-bond-market-than-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 19:25:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国国税局向肯·格里芬道歉，以和解税务数据泄露案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/irs-apologizes-to-ken-griffin-to-settle-tax-data-breach-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国税局向对冲基金经理肯·格里芬公开道歉，原因是他未能保护好自己的机密税务数据，防止其被一名现已入狱的承包商窃取并泄露给媒体。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/irs-apologizes-to-ken-griffin-to-settle-tax-data-breach-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 19:16:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰与俄罗斯今年通过阿联酋完成第五次囚犯交换</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/ukraine-russia-complete-fifth-prisoner-swap-this-year-via-uae</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰与俄罗斯周二完成大规模囚犯交换，这是由阿拉伯联合酋长国斡旋的自 2022 年以来两个交战国之间达成的罕见协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/ukraine-russia-complete-fifth-prisoner-swap-this-year-via-uae</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 19:15:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚总统部署军队制止“叛国”抗议活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/kenyan-president-deploys-military-to-halt-treasonous-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚总统威廉·鲁托部署军队，结束全国范围内“叛国”的反政府抗议活动，该抗议活动造成至少 5 人死亡，数十人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/kenyan-president-deploys-military-to-halt-treasonous-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 18:59:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>秘鲁解决与中国港口争端 总统准备会见习近平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/peru-resolves-chinese-port-spat-as-president-prepares-to-meet-xi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，在两国总统会晤之前，秘鲁与一家中国国有企业就一个价值 13 亿美元的大型港口的商业模式达成了和解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/peru-resolves-chinese-port-spat-as-president-prepares-to-meet-xi</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 18:52:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SpaceX 猎鹰重型火箭将发射美国卫星追踪太阳风暴</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/spacex-s-falcon-heavy-to-launch-us-satellite-to-track-sun-storms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[SpaceX 的猎鹰重型火箭是世界上最强大的运载火箭之一，它将于周二发射，将一颗新的美国卫星送入轨道，该卫星旨在帮助气象预报员监测大规模太阳风暴。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/spacex-s-falcon-heavy-to-launch-us-satellite-to-track-sun-storms</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 18:47:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗将如何选举总统，以及他为何重要</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/iran-election-who-will-succeed-president-raisi-and-how-will-they-be-chosen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗定于 6 月 28 日举行总统大选，此前易卜拉欣·莱西在一次直升机坠毁事故中丧生。虽然伊朗的最高权力掌握在最高领袖阿亚图拉·阿里·哈梅内伊手中，但总统有时可以利用民众支持、政治关系和与强大机构的联系来影响政策。此次选举正值伊朗与西方关系紧张之际，德黑兰动员了一个地区代理民兵网络来打击]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/iran-election-who-will-succeed-president-raisi-and-how-will-they-be-chosen</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 18:36:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在总统辩论前放宽禁言令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/trump-gag-order-relaxed-in-hush-money-case-after-trial-loss</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约封口费案中针对唐纳德·特朗普的禁言令基本被解除，这让这位前总统在竞选总统期间有了更多的自由来批评诉讼程序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/trump-gag-order-relaxed-in-hush-money-case-after-trial-loss</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 17:55:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利针对反腐监督机构和调查媒体展开调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/hungary-launches-probe-against-graft-watchdog-in-orban-crackdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班设立的一个国家机构已开始对反腐监督机构透明国际和一家新闻网站进行调查，这是针对批评其政权的团体的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/hungary-launches-probe-against-graft-watchdog-in-orban-crackdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 14:40:50 GMT</pubDate>
